Business Brief -- Sport Supply Group Inc.:
   PaineWebber Hired to Deal
   With Acquisition Inquiries
The company, which has 4.6 million shares outstanding, is
27%-owned by BSN Corp., a sporting goods concern also in
Dallas, and made its initial public offering last year. Sport
Supply was quoted at $9.125, up 25 cents, in American Stock
Exchange trading yesterday, putting the company's market
value at $42 million.